<%- include("partials/materio-head", { title }) %>
  <% const safeSearchQuery = typeof searchQuery !== "undefined" ? searchQuery : ""; %>
  <body>
    <div class="layout-wrapper layout-content-navbar">
      <div class="layout-container">
        <%- include("partials/materio-sidebar", { activePage }) %>
        <div class="layout-page">
          <%- include("partials/materio-navbar", { title, searchQuery: safeSearchQuery }) %>
          <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="container-xxl flex-grow-1 container-p-y">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <h5 class="mb-0">Ve hoa lan</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="mb-0">
                    Hoa lan tu lau duoc xem la mot trong nhung loai hoa dep va quy phai nhat trong the gioi
                    thuc vat. Ve dep tinh te, da dang mau sac va hinh dang giup hoa lan tro thanh lua chon
                    yeu thich cua nguoi choi hoa. Khong chi dep, hoa lan con mang y nghia ve su thanh tao, may
                    man va thinh vuong. Viec cham soc hoa lan can su kien nhan va hieu biet, nhung doi lai la
                    trai nghiem thu vi va thu gian.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <%- include("partials/materio-footer") %>
            <div class="content-backdrop fade"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="layout-overlay layout-menu-toggle"></div>
    </div>
<%- include("partials/materio-scripts") %>
